&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-2817&quot; title=&quot;Closing an unconnected SslTransport get an invalid close state exception&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-2817&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-2817&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;; Check if socketChannel is connected in `SslTransportLayer.close`&lt;/p&gt;

