&lt;p&gt;    This closes #511&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;commit 36bd18b0d6b1de88f06227f90fdc020611330964&lt;br/&gt;
Author: Ismael Juma &amp;lt;ismael@juma.me.uk&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
